metadata.name: #01 - Frogsleep
metadata.description:
Greencloud is a world created by Lucas Dillon that brings together image making and audio to explore an environment with it’s own laws, traditions and ecosystem. 

Greencloud is an ever evolving landscape that exists between physical and digital processing. All works evolve from charcoal drawings. Each frame is like a box with in a comic strip, a narrative with in a larger narrative. 

Please enjoy your trip.

#01 - Frogsleep
3000 × 2400
8 second loop
